name: SnackboxAI
description: The ultimate link-in-bio solution geared around the unique needs of the web3 industry. Custom chatbot, token swaps, gated content and more. SNACKBOX offers a streamlined web3 link-in-bio solution exclusively for token projects and influencers, centralizing project information and providing a one-stop shop for learning about and engaging with web3 projects. By delivering all the resources, a chatbot to answer any question, and a swap token component, we believe our link-in-bio will significantly enhance the user experience and facilitate the conversion of potential buyers into committed token holders. We aim to redefine how web3 projects and influencers interact with their communities and drive engagement.
